{"tid":2033100,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"今日啲感覺返曬泥","createTime":"2020-05-24T12:31:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T12:33:11.000Z","uid":199391,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"618fe960b42e9a3df36352071deccd415001210b","tid":2033100,"uid":199391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T12:31:36.000Z","msg":"隔左一段時間再重現街頭戰，雖然今日目的唔係要同狗打，但係今日feel到係近期嘅一大轉變，開始趨向主流咁推祟建國、獨立。<br />\n<br />\n雖然冇得同612比，因為今日有部分人有唔同顧慮而冇出到泥，但係希望無論係啱啱先醒覺嘅人、近期對場運動感到灰鳩嘅人、愈打愈撚起勁嘅人，由今日開始重拾返呢份熱誠，記住只有獨立先有民主。<br />\n<br />\n民族自決，香港獨立<br />\n27號見<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DWZbDrE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDWZbDrE.png&h=f242e891&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"62c27f2aa813a67d626324bc77cb3c8d7b8dd5be","tid":2033100,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T12:33:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}